Order of activities via cron job:

  1. Fetch all feeds and process into Recommendations
  2. Register new MythTV recording schedules for any recommendations which are < 2 days old,
     have EPG matches, and which do not have an existing recording schedules
  3. Check to see if any recordings have been made of previous recommendations
  4. Cancel recording schedules made by recommendations which have had one recorded program?
     This should be optional
  